quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  17,18,"On taw…óo no faandii yaccinaneede=yaawnaneede, Men yaccinanay mo ton huunde ko Men muuyi, wonannde on mo Men yi…ói, refti Men wa…óana mo Jahannama, o naatoya nge ko o ≈ãi√±aa…óo, pottinaa…óo [yurmeende]"
  17,19,"On faalaa…óo laakara, o gollani ngal golle maggal, hara kanko ko o gom…óin…óo ;…ìen …óon, golle ma…ì…ìe …óen wonii jaarnaa…óe"
  17,20,"Kala (ma…ì…ìe),Me…óen …ìeydana ; …ìee …óoo e …ìee …óoo, immorde e dokkal Joomi maa. Dokkal Joomi maa ngal wonaali ha…óaa ngal"
  17,21,"Ndaarii no Men …ìurniri yoga ma…ì…ìe e dow yoga, ko laakara on …ìuri mawnude darjaaji,…ìuri mawnude kadi …ìural"
  17,22,Wata a wa…óidan Alla rewetee…óo goo ; joo…óoyo…óaa ko a ≈ãi√±aa…óo woppaa…óo
  17,23,"Joomi maa yamirii :\"Wata on rewu ko wanaa Kanko, jibim…ìe …ìen,mo∆¥∆¥agol [e ma…ì…ìe]:si nayewu go…ó…óo e ma…ì…ìe yottike ma,maa …óum …ìe …ói…óo non;wata a wi‚Äôan …ìe \"bis=uf!\" wata a wikko …ìe =wota a furo,wowlan …ìe konngol teddungol"
  17,24,"Yankinano…óaa …ìe yurme…óaa …ìe, wi‚Äôaa: ¬´ Joomi an, yurme …ìe‚Äôe, wano …ìe ne‚Äôirnoo lan non hari ko mi tosokun ¬ª"
  17,25,"Joomi mo'on no Anndi ko woni ka nder wonkiiji mon, si tawii on wonuno mo∆¥∆¥u…ìe ; pellet Kanko O wonanii ruttotoo…ìe …ìen Surroowo"
  17,26,"Jonnu jom …ìadondiral haqqee makko on, e …ìillii…óo, e seteejo haqqee makko on ; wata a funsu funsudee"
  17,27,"Pellet funsoo…ìe …ìen, ko si…ó…ìe seytanuuji …óin ; seytaane non wonii yeddu…óo Joomi mun"
